This is for Macintosh only

- gnotify.rb 
pnotify.rb is a script for Weechat that sends highlight notifications and private messages to the Growl notification framework. 
see http://growl.info/
It uses the ruby gem meow.

sudo gem install meow
cp gnotify.rb ~/.weechat/ruby/autoload/
mkdir ~/.weechat/images/
cp images/weechat.png ~/.weechat/images/


- pnotify.rb 
pnotify.rb is a script for Weechat that sends highlight notifications and private messages to the Prowl notification API.
see http://prowl.weks.net/
It uses the ruby gem prowl

sudo gem install prowl
cp pnotify.rb ~/.weechat/ruby/autoload/
